Interface TransactionMapper

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractTransactionMapper, AbstractTransactionMapper, AccountAddressRestrictionTransactionMapper, AccountAddressRestrictionTransactionMapper, AccountMosaicRestrictionTransactionMapper, AccountMosaicRestrictionTransactionMapper, AccountOperationRestrictionTransactionMapper, AccountOperationRestrictionTransactionMapper, GeneralTransactionMapper, GeneralTransactionMapper, NodeKeyLinkTransactionMapper, NodeKeyLinkTransactionMapper, VotingKeyLinkTransactionMapper, VotingKeyLinkTransactionMapper, VrfKeyLinkTransactionMapper, VrfKeyLinkTransactionMapper

    public interface TransactionMapper
    A transaction mapper knows how to map DTO for standard and embedded transactions into a Transaction object.
